{% comment %}
  custom-hero.liquid
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  KICK-inspired hero: contain the (normally full-bleed) hero media to the page
  width and give it rounded corners, so it reads as a contained card.
  Keeps the existing content layout.

  Background: the band/gutters behind the rounded card now follow the hero
  section's own "Color scheme" setting (editable in the Theme Editor). We no
  longer force it transparent — that override hid the color-scheme background
  and made the hero background look non-editable.

  To revert: delete this file and its {% render %} call in sections/hero.liquid.
{% endcomment %}
<style>
  /* Background comes from the section's Color scheme (editable in the admin).
     The rounded card floats on top of whatever background color is chosen. */
  .hero .hero__container {
    width: min(var(--page-content-width), 100% - var(--page-margin) * 2);
    margin-inline: auto;
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .hero .hero__container {
      border-radius: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
